<h1>Lionel Andres Messi Cuccittini!</h1>
</center>
<h2> The early life of Messi </h2>
<p> Messi was born in Santa Fe Province(Rosario,Argentina)on 24th June 1986.His father(Jorge Messi) was a steel worker and his mother(Celia Maria Cuccittini)a cleaner.He grew up in a family where football was adored.At a young age he started playing football with his elder brothers.After his parents saw that he has interest in football,they put him in the local club,Grandoli,before moving on to another club called Newell's Old Boys.The coach of Grandoli was his father but his grandmother accompanied him to his matches and training.</p>
<h3> How did Messi start playing football for Barcelona? </h3>
<p>When he was 13,his parents had to move to Barcelona,so he had to change his team.He tried playing for the under 14 Barcelona team and was probably the best of them all.Barcelona were amazed by the skills of just a 13 year old.He quickly graduated from lower levels and became a part of the main team when he was 16 and had his debut in a friendly match.
